{"tid":627401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係好有重要性咩？] 本周最佳陣容　對唔住冇C朗","createTime":"2018-04-13T02:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T03:31:44.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eebaf7473f339f6deebbc8f9678b7ca1d9ddc776","tid":627401,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180412/photo/bkn-20180412233250714-0412_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180413003549\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180412%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180412233250714-0412_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180413003549&h=cdb30054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今輪歐聯8強次回合睇到個人心都離埋，羅馬、祖雲達斯大打爭氣波，反過來睇巴塞同皇馬就冇料到，所以歐洲足協公布本周最佳陣容亦告大洗牌，今個禮拜冇美斯同蘇亞雷斯都正路，事實上佢哋係踢得差，就連最佳陣容常客C朗今次都唔入圍，最佳陣容如下： <br />\n<br />\n門將:大衞蘇利亞(西維爾) <br />\n後衞:高拉洛夫(羅馬)、曉姆斯(拜仁慕尼黑)、查維馬天尼斯(拜仁慕尼黑)、基文迪朗格勒(西維爾)、文迪奴斯(羅馬) <br />\n中場:馬度迪(祖雲達斯)、迪羅斯(羅馬) <br />\n前鋒:文迪蘇傑(祖雲達斯)、迪斯高(羅馬)、穆罕默德沙拿"},{"pid":"d124f1cac4657275220c8d7b129eba96ea4fee6f","tid":627401,"uid":2500,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"對唔住無美斯"},{"pid":"3cab5b6dd426394c943b74d3d69b3c5c74bcabd9","tid":627401,"uid":34806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"即係只要柒朗好有重要性<br />\n四場波其他人就會自動變左無重要性？"},{"pid":"c67336e1455cf53f53ad1f2420933cd5166d0609","tid":627401,"uid":22999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"隔離個球王都冇份wo，唔好意思"},{"pid":"f7ef1c3178ae80e17a140a2d84199463ecdd50b4","tid":627401,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"點解成鳩日拎fantasy隻game當round最高分11人就當係最佳陣容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}